TLCConcept.showAs: Animal Welfare (Import of Dogs, Cats and Ferrets) Bill

longTitle.p: Make provision for and in connection with restricting the importation and non-commercial movement of dogs, cats and ferrets.

formula.name: enactingText
formula.p: Be it enacted the King’s most Excellent Majesty, by and with the advice and consent of the Lords Spiritual and Temporal, and Commons, in this present

content.p: Parliament assembled, and by the authority of the same, as follows:—
